  <brief_title>Study of Sc-FOS for Pouchitis Prevention</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevention of Pouchitis With Short-Chain Fructooligosaccharide Therapy, A Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Trial</official_title>
