  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective is to compare prebiotic therapy with placebo for the prevention of
      pouchitis after closure of diverting ileostomy in patients with an ileal pouch anal
      anastomosis. This study will also characterize the effects of prebiotics on the fecal
      microbiota and fecal microbial metabolites and correlate these effects with the primary
      outcome of development of pouchitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
